title: Kerry Howley to read on Oct. 29 from well-received book on fighting (Roosevelt University)
text: ( Source : Roosevelt University ) Posted: 10/22/ 2015 Writer Kerry Howley , author of the book-length essay Thrown, will read and discuss her work at 5 p.m. on Thursday, Oct. 29 in Room 700 of Roosevelt University's Gage Building , 18 S. Michigan
